\section{Size of Tree is One Less than Order}
Tags: Size of Tree is One Less than Order, Tree Theory, Graph Theory, Trees

\begin{theorem}
Let $T$ be a connected simple graph of order $n$.
Then $T$ is a tree {{Iff}} the size of $T$ is $n-1$.
\end{theorem}

