\section{Size of Tree is One Less than Order/Necessary Condition}
Tags: Size of Tree is One Less than Order, Tree Theory, Trees

\begin{theorem}
Let $T$ be a tree of order $n$.
Then the size of $T$ is $n-1$.
\end{theorem}
